WEBVTT

15:57.310 --> 15:58.710 line:80%
The snow is thicker here.

15:59.040 --> 16:00.310 line:80%
Why didn't you answer when I called you?

16:00.310 --> 16:01.830 line:80%
I couldn't find you anywhere
along the way.

16:01.830 --> 16:03.690 line:80%
Do you know you scared me to death?

16:04.000 --> 16:05.550 line:80%
It's okay. We found them now.

16:05.550 --> 16:06.810 line:80%
Kids just love to play.
